review_title: review_title: Stunning glasses, stellar customer service!
text:
text: Having to succumb to age is never fun, but these gorgeous glasses made it more bearable. I actually enjoy wearing them because they are so cute! The bejeweled sides make me feel at least a little more youthful! And they appear to be great quality.
I have to mention the customer service, which is BEYOND perfection. I tried to figure out my own script (mistake, I know) and realized I got it much too strong. The glasses had not yet shipped so I contacted the seller to see if they could update it to a lesser strength. No problem, they said. Unfortunately, I still received the script I had initially ordered. My mistake, of course. I thought I‚Äôd just let them know, but in no way expected the response I received. Not only did they apologize, but they immediately sent me a second pair of glasses with the lesser script and told me not to worry about returning the first. I was so pleasantly surprised and these work great! I am using them as I type this up. The packaging is also beautiful and comes with a sweet thank you sticker that shows they truly care about their customers. Just a great company and a great touch. Thank you for standing above and beyond in customer service. As I transition from this script I plan to only purchase from you!
